        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer742380020" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7458513105723343241">I know that this is popular and I get what the book is trying to say about not worrying about what other people think, but I was freaking terrified of this book when I was a kid. In fact, I&apos;m still creeped out to this day. The visuals and some of the stuff that happened to the main character was just terrifying. <br/><br/>It&apos;s not a bad book, it really isn&apos;t, but it scared the crap out of me and I will not go anywhere <b>NEAR</b> that book. So a big round of applause to you who love this book, cuz I sure as hell</span>
  <span id="freeText7458513105723343241" style="display:none">I know that this is popular and I get what the book is trying to say about not worrying about what other people think, but I was freaking terrified of this book when I was a kid. In fact, I'm still creeped out to this day. The visuals and some of the stuff that happened to the main character was just terrifying. <br /><br />It's not a bad book, it really isn't, but it scared the crap out of me and I will not go anywhere <b>NEAR</b> that book. So a big round of applause to you who love this book, cuz I sure as hell didn't. </span>
