        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer653649095" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14356012481813584290">What an absolutely wonderful book! Such an original idea that teaches such a simple lesson! And the illustrations were so detailed! This is definitely one I&apos;ll be adding to our library when I get the chance. Probably a level 3 or 4 reading level at least, but something a parent would enjoy reading to a kid of any age. Camilla is scared what people will think of her on her first day of school, but it turns out she doesn&apos;t need to worry because she comes down with a case of the stripes, her whole </span>
  <span id="freeText14356012481813584290" style="display:none">What an absolutely wonderful book! Such an original idea that teaches such a simple lesson! And the illustrations were so detailed! This is definitely one I'll be adding to our library when I get the chance. Probably a level 3 or 4 reading level at least, but something a parent would enjoy reading to a kid of any age. Camilla is scared what people will think of her on her first day of school, but it turns out she doesn't need to worry because she comes down with a case of the stripes, her whole body looking like a brightly colored rainbow. Halfway through reading this with my children I felt like the kid in the back of the class that's going "Ooh! Ohh! I know what's gonna happen!" as I frantically wave my hand. (Why do I get an image of Horshack and the sweathogs when I say that, and jeez, did that date me?) Anyway, we loved this book, and highly recommend it.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14356012481813584290" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
