<div id="review_30964792" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/30964792" />
    <a title="Lisa  (not getting friends updates) Vegan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan"><img alt="Lisa  (not getting friends updates) Vegan" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1243394822p2/83445.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/30964792?book_show_action=true">Aug 22, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lisa  (not getting friends updates) Vegan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lisa  (not getting friends updates) Vegan" href="/user/show/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan">Lisa  (not getting friends updates) Vegan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780590929974" href="/book/show/1137392.A_Bad_Case_of_Stripes">review of another edition</a>

          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">all early elementary school kids and older preschoolers</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=childrens">childrens</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=readbooks-male-author-or-illust">readbooks-male-author-or-illust</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=picture-books">picture-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=zz-4star">zz-4star</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=reviewed">reviewed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=z2008">z2008</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer30964792" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6011008712733716275">This is a fun and colorful, very colorful!, book with a great message about not being afraid to be true to yourself and not caring so much about what other people think of you. It uses humor in a way that’s fun for kids, and the moral is clear but doesn’t overpower the story. The story seemed to end slightly too abruptly to me, but overall it was very enjoyable.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


