        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1334776281" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17261397544293984309">Wow. The artwork for this is really nice, but the message is what really struck me as amazing. The story is basically about how conformity destroys your individuality. In simpler terms, not doing something you really love because everyone thinks it&apos;s weird (like eating lima beans) turns you into something you&apos;re not (like a striped girl with a tail and tree trunk legs). Such a great story.</span>
  <span id="freeText17261397544293984309" style="display:none">Wow. The artwork for this is really nice, but the message is what really struck me as amazing. The story is basically about how conformity destroys your individuality. In simpler terms, not doing something you really love because everyone thinks it's weird (like eating lima beans) turns you into something you're not (like a striped girl with a tail and tree trunk legs). Such a great story.</span>
  <a data-text-id="17261397544293984309" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
